Type locality.
Hydrothermal vent in the Manus Back-Arc Basin, Western Pacific (151°51'52.328''E, 3°40'47.684''S, 
1940 m
). Most specimens were collected in the surrounding areas of the mussel (

Bathymodiolus manusensis
Hashimoto & Furuta, 2007

) bed and the community of tube-worms (

Arcovestia ivanovi
Southward & Galkin, 1997

).

